General.Name: Ikena Oncology Inc
General.Description: Ikena Oncology, Inc., an oncology company, focuses on developing therapies for patients in need that target nodes of cancer growth, spread, and therapeutic resistance. It develops IK-595, a molecular glue designed to trap MEK and RAF in an inactive complex. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Boston, Massachusetts.
